that I had with Tom.

23:23.424 --> 23:27.087
<i>You know that Tom</i>
<i>talked me into goin'to MIT?</i>

23:27.161 --> 23:30.597
Really? Uh, no.
I didn't know that.
<i>Yeah.</i>

23:30.664 --> 23:33.360
Yeah, I remembered
when I was talkin' with Chris.

23:33.434 --> 23:36.961
Hey, tomorrow you're on
the <i>Earthquake</i> set.

23:37.038 --> 23:40.064
<i>Chuck Heston, Lorne Greene and...</i>

23:40.141 --> 23:42.541
Ava Gardner.

23:42.610 --> 23:47.570
Yeah, I know, Ava Gardner.
And I'm supposed to be doing a stunt,
and I don't even know what it is.

23:47.648 --> 23:49.809
Wha-What, the stunt?

23:49.884 --> 23:53.752
- Yeah.
- Oh, I hear it's-it's just a little fall.

23:58.826 --> 24:01.795
<i>This is a little fall?</i>

24:01.862 --> 24:03.955
Well, for a stuntman.

