<i>We're almost ready!</i>

24:06.534 --> 24:10.595
Look, Al, I-I-- I don't--
I don't think I can do this.

24:10.671 --> 24:13.367
Well, you got to
if you wanna leap outta here.

24:13.441 --> 24:15.432
To what, my death?

