Hi.

24:21.115 --> 24:23.640
Is that all you have to say,
Chad?

24:25.686 --> 24:27.677
Uh--

24:30.424 --> 24:32.858
You don't remember me,
do you?

24:32.927 --> 24:35.589
Wrap party,
<i>Poseidon Adventure.</i>

24:36.597 --> 24:39.259
I came as a giant clam.
You were Aquaman.

24:39.333 --> 24:42.393
I-I'm sor-- I don't remember.

24:45.873 --> 24:49.331
<i>[ Man On Bullhorn ]</i>
<i>Take two. Background. And action!</i>

24:49.410 --> 24:52.436
Maybe you were the flying fish.
Hey!

24:52.513 --> 24:54.879
What?
[ Screams ]

24:54.949 --> 24:56.940
Aa-aah!

25:01.722 --> 25:03.713
Help!

25:08.162 --> 25:10.153
<i>[ Crowd Chattering ]</i>
Al!

25:12.266 --> 25:15.326
Help!

25:18.239 --> 25:20.537
[ Yelps ]

25:22.042 --> 25:24.033
It's Ben!

25:24.111 --> 25:28.707
It's Ben Cartwright!
Sam! Look, look! It's Ben Cartwright!

25:28.782 --> 25:32.912
- Al!
- [ Man ] Ooh! Step back.

25:32.987 --> 25:37.924
Sam, hang on!
Ben Cartwright is gonna save you.
I don't believe it!

25:41.896 --> 25:43.386
Uh-oh.

25:43.464 --> 25:46.058
[ Screams ]

25:54.074 --> 25:56.872
Yeah! Yeah!
You looked great!

25:56.944 --> 26:00.402
That was great.
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>He did it again, huh?</i>

26:00.481 --> 26:02.779
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>Yeah.</i>

26:02.850 --> 26:07.412
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>Not bad.</i>
Chad, you okay, guy?

26:07.488 --> 26:09.479
Huh? You okay?

26:09.557 --> 26:11.855
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>He's clear. Let's flatten the air bag.</i>

26:17.798 --> 26:20.767
Once a screamer,
always a screamer.

26:21.769 --> 26:23.828
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>Don't throw that open!</i>

26:29.009 --> 26:31.341
<i>Get the best boy over here</i>
<i>to hook this up.</i>

26:44.225 --> 26:47.422
Look, Chris--
I could have done it!
Had my card right now!

26:47.494 --> 26:50.224
Is that what you want?
Your stuntman's card?

26:50.297 --> 26:54.495
What do you think I've been
workin' for all this time?
I thought it was your music.

26:54.568 --> 26:57.662
Music!
What in the hell you talkin' about?
Music's just for kicks.

26:57.738 --> 27:00.138
Look, what I heard last night
wasn't for kicks.

27:00.207 --> 27:04.166
Yeah, right.
Can you see me telling Dad
I'm gonna be a musician?

27:04.245 --> 27:07.442
Dad? Come on. It's your life, not his.

27:07.514 --> 27:12.076
Listen to you!
What've you been doin'
the last few years?

27:12.152 --> 27:14.746
Yeah, well, that-- that's me.

27:14.822 --> 27:19.691
I mean, uh, it's-it's what I love to do,
but it isn't you.
You've been playing guitar.

27:19.760 --> 27:24.254
<i>Look,you wanna make Dad proud?</i>
<i>Then do what you do best.</i>

27:24.331 --> 27:27.698
It'll take a lot more courage
than jumping off buildings.

27:29.937 --> 27:33.202
Yeah. But what do I know
about the music business?

27:36.176 --> 27:39.111
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>(music) By the dark of the moon (music)</i>

27:42.082 --> 27:45.210
(music) But there came an early snow (music)
