27:45.286 --> 27:50.223
<i>[ Traci ]</i>
<i>Mort Greenblatt. He's the A&R V.P.</i>
<i>on our country and western label.</i>

27:50.291 --> 27:53.988
<i>Hm! The only Texas cowpoke</i>
<i>ever born in Brooklyn.</i>

27:54.061 --> 27:55.995
[ Both Laugh ]

27:56.063 --> 28:00.227
He's kind of a sleaze-ball,
but he can make things happen.

28:00.301 --> 28:04.897
Thank you for doin' this for Chris.
Oh, I didn't do it for Chris.

28:07.241 --> 28:10.506
[ Chuckles ]
See you Saturday.

