28:28.262 --> 28:31.026
Where's Dad?
Don't worry. He'll be here.

28:31.098 --> 28:33.089
<i>(music) [ Continues, Indistinct ]</i>
He's up next.

28:33.167 --> 28:35.727
Yeah, yeah. Okay.

28:35.803 --> 28:39.569
<i>(music) But there came an early snow (music)</i>

28:41.275 --> 28:46.269
Dad?
<i>(music)</i>  <i>There's a hoot owl howlin'</i>
<i>outside my window now (music)</i>

28:46.347 --> 28:50.181
Dad.
Hey, big time.

28:50.250 --> 28:52.912
How long have you been in here?

28:52.986 --> 28:54.977
About a six-pack.

28:56.256 --> 29:00.283
Come on. Chris is on.
I can hear him just fine from here.

29:00.361 --> 29:03.524
All he wants is to
make you proud of him.
Oh, I am proud.

29:03.597 --> 29:07.465
Then show him.
Go in there where he can see you.

29:07.534 --> 29:12.062
<i>(music)</i>  <i>We'll be ridin' Wildfire (music)</i>

29:12.139 --> 29:15.108
Why are you doin' this?

29:15.175 --> 29:18.144
What have you got against him?
[ Sighs ]

29:19.680 --> 29:22.114
He got born weak.

29:22.182 --> 29:26.380
What?
Weak. Premature.

29:26.453 --> 29:28.853
After your mom and I split,

29:28.922 --> 29:31.550
she raised him all wrong.

29:31.625 --> 29:33.957
I'm gonna make a man out of him.

29:37.598 --> 29:39.623
That's great, Dad.
