29:39.700 --> 29:42.828
<i>[ Applause ]</i>
<i>[ Man On P.A.]</i>
<i>Next up is a young man from Montana,</i>

29:42.903 --> 29:45.133
<i>just been out to Hollywood</i>
<i>less than a year.</i>

29:45.205 --> 29:47.571
<i>Please welcome to the stage</i>
<i>Chris Stone!</i>

29:47.641 --> 29:49.632
<i>[ Applause ]</i>

